<SYNC Start=8380><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=9140><P Class=KRCC>
여기, 일루 와
<SYNC Start=10440><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10440><P Class=KRCC>
