<SYNC Start=12440><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=22740><P Class=KRCC>
내 차례야, 내 차례
<SYNC Start=24920><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=28140><P Class=KRCC>
